Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:53.17,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HBE474B&}You locked me into the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.17,0:22:55.34,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HBE474B&}I’m your preserved flower
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.34,0:22:59.01,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HBE474B&}The world is too slow to understand
